text: Jade Winston Dernbach (born 3 March 1986 in Johannesburg, South Africa) is an English-Italian former cricketer who has played 24 one-day internationals and 40 Twenty20 Internationals for England and Italy. ==Other websites== * * Surrey County Cricket Club Player Profile Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:English and Welsh cricketers Category:Italian cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Johannesburg
title: Jade Dernbach
